                        <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center"><em class="icon ni ni-chat-circle mr-2"></em> Kurban</a></li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center"><em class="icon ni ni-chat-circle mr-2"></em> Helal ve Haramlar</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center"><em class="icon ni ni-chat-circle mr-2"></em> Helal Ürün ve Hizmet</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center"><em class="icon ni ni-chat-circle mr-2"></em> Adak ve Yemin</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center"><em class="icon ni ni-chat-circle mr-2"></em> İbadet, Dua, Tövbe</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center"><em class="icon ni ni-chat-circle mr-2"></em> Kur'an-ı Kerim'in Muhtevası, İcazı ve Tarihi</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center"><em class="icon ni ni-chat-circle mr-2"></em> Aile Hayatı</a></li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center"><em class="icon ni ni-chat-circle mr-2"></em> Tasavvuf</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="flex items-center"><em class="icon ni ni-chat-circle mr-2"></em> Dini-Milli Gün ve Geceler</a></li>
